'''Mojmír Chytil''' (born 29 April 1999) is a Czech professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[forward (association football)|forward]] for [[SK Slavia Prague|Slavia Prague]] and the [[Czech Republic national football team|Czech Republic national team]].

==Early life==
Chytil was born in [[Skalka (Prostějov District)|Skalka]] in the [[Olomouc Region]].<ref>{{Cite web|first=Michal|last=Kvasnica|title=Chytil zaujal reprezentaci i ligu: rozlučka s Olomoucí, smlouva tlačí|trans-title=Chytil impressed the national team and the league: farewell to Olomouc, contract pressing|url=https://isport.blesk.cz/clanek/fotbal-reprezentace/423079/chytil-zaujal-reprezentaci-i-ligu-rozlucka-s-olomouci-smlouva-tlaci.html|website=[[Blesk]]|date=16 November 2022|language=cs}}</ref>

==Club career==
===Sigma Olomouc===
Chytil made his professional debut for [[Sigma Olomouc]] in 2018.<ref>{{Cite news|first=Jan|last=Dočkal|title=Chytil je po návratu olomoucký hrot číslo jedna: Pardubice mi hodně pomohly|url=https://www.idnes.cz/fotbal/prvni-liga/olomouc-fotbal-chytil.A220218_152220_fotbal_ald|website=[[Mladá fronta Dnes]]|publisher=[[Mafra (company)|Mafra]]|date=19 February 2022|access-date=17 November 2022|language=cs}}</ref> He was sent on loan to [[FK Pardubice|Pardubice]] during the [[2021–22 Czech First League]], scoring five goals.<ref>{{Cite news|first=Marek|last=Votke|title=Chytil po loučení s Pardubicemi: Nechám si zarámovat dres|url=https://www.idnes.cz/fotbal/prvni-liga/chytil-po-louceni-s-pardubicemi-necham-si-zaramovat-dres.A211220_642501_fotbal_rou|website=Mladá fronta Dnes|publisher=Mafra|date=20 December 2021|access-date=17 November 2022|language=cs}}</ref> This loan caused then-coach of Sigma Olomouc Jiří Krejčí to regret Chytil's departure.<ref>{{Cite news|first=Marek|last=Votke|title=Nechceme žádnou loterii. Sportovní ředitel Pardubic odkrývá přestupové plány|url=https://www.idnes.cz/fotbal/prvni-liga/fk-pardubice-prestupove-obdobi-posily.A221109_691561_fotbal_mama|website=Mladá fronta Dnes|publisher=Mafra|date=9 November 2022|access-date=17 November 2022|language=cs}}</ref> In the [[2022–23 Czech First League]] season, Chytil helped Sigma Olomouc to finish sixth place.<ref>{{Cite news|first=Jan|last=Dočkal|title=Chytilovo půlroční odcházení do Slavie. Vyplatilo se Sigmě?|url=https://www.idnes.cz/fotbal/prvni-liga/mojmir-chytil-odchazeni-sigma-olomouc.A230525_727408_fotbal_ten|website=Mladá fronta Dnes|publisher=Mafra|date=25 May 2023|access-date=23 July 2023|language=cs}}</ref>

===Slavia Prague===
Chytil signed for [[SK Slavia Prague|Slavia Prague]] at the end of May 2023,<ref>{{Cite news|first=Miloslav|last=Novák|title=Chytil je už slávistou. Chtěl jsem ho pro hru ve vápně a zády k bráně, říká kouč|url=https://www.idnes.cz/fotbal/prvni-liga/mojmir-chytil-slavia-sigma-olomouc-prestup-smlouva-na-ctyri-roky.A230529_131238_fotbal_min|website=Mladá fronta Dnes|publisher=Mafra|date=29 May 2023|access-date=23 July 2023|language=cs}}</ref> signing a contract until June 2027.<ref>{{Cite news|first=David|last=Jahoda|title=Oficiálně potvrzeno. Útočník Mojmír Chytil v Sigmě končí, nově bude oblékat dres pražské Slavie|url=https://olomouc.rozhlas.cz/oficialne-potvrzeno-utocnik-mojmir-chytil-v-sigme-konci-nove-bude-oblekat-dres-9002436|website=ČRo Olomouc|publisher=[[Czech Radio]]|location=Olomouc|date=29 May 2023|access-date=23 July 2023|language=cs}}</ref> He scored on his debut for the club, a 2–0 win against [[FC Hradec Králové|Hradec Králové]], in the first game of the [[2023–24 Czech First League]].<ref>{{Cite news|first=Lukáš|last=Michalík|title=Vyšlo to skvěle.' Chytila po debutu dresu Slavie těšil gól, ale i kamarádi z vesnice. Spokojený byl i kouč|url=https://www.irozhlas.cz/sport/fotbal/mojmir-chytil-premiera-v-dresu-slavie-gol-hradci_2307230745_mim|website=Český rozhlas|publisher=[[Czech Radio]]|date=23 July 2023|access-date=10 May 2025|language=cs}}</ref> A week later, Chytil set up Slavia's second goal, and scored their third, in a 3–1 win against [[SK Dynamo České Budějovice|České Budějovice]].<ref>{{Cite news|first=Pavel|last=Kortus|title=Loni bychom podobný zápas nevyhráli, odhadl Trpišovský. Ocenil Chytila|url=https://www.idnes.cz/fotbal/prvni-liga/trpisovsky-slavia-budejovice-fotbal-prvni-liga-chytil-provod.A230730_171116_budejovice-sport_pkr|website=[[Mladá fronta Dnes]]|publisher=[[Mafra (company)|Mafra]]|date=30 July 2023|access-date=10 May 2025|language=cs}}</ref> Following his strong start to the season, Chytil was named the league's Player of the Month for July 2023, voted for by fans.<ref>{{cite web |title=Chytil byl podle fanoušků nejlepším hráčem uplynulého měsíce, trenérům vládl Frťala |url=https://sport.ceskatelevize.cz/clanek/fotbal/1-liga/chytil-byl-podle-fanousku-nejlepsim-hracem-uplynuleho-mesice-trenerum-vladl-frtala/64ccd946b923c8c51f6b4323 |website=[[Czech Television]] |access-date=10 May 2025 |language=cs |date=4 August 2023}}</ref>

==International career==
Having represented the Czech Republic at under-17 and under-20 level,<ref name=wf/> Chytil received his first call-up to the [[Czech Republic national football team|Czech Republic senior squad]] in November 2022.<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mojmír Chytil: Z nominace jsem nadšený|trans-title=Mojmír Chytil: I am excited about the call-up|url=https://repre.fotbal.cz/mojmir-chytil-z-nominace-jsem-nadseny/a17357|website=[[Football Association of the Czech Republic]]|date=14 November 2022|access-date=16 November 2022|language=cs}}</ref> He debuted with a [[hat-trick]] in a [[UEFA Euro 2024 qualifying]] against the [[Faroe Islands national football team|Faroe Islands]], ending in a 5–1 victory for the Czechs.<ref>{{Cite news|first=Michal|last=Muzikant|title=Chytil jako Bican: Byl jsem dojatý. Na zápisné si po hattricku asi půjčím|url=https://www.denik.cz/fotbal/chytil-jako-bican-byl-jsem-dojaty-na-zapisne-si-po-hattricku-asi-pujcim-20221116.html|website=[[Deník]]|publisher=Vltave Labe Media|date=16 November 2022|access-date=17 November 2022|language=cs}}</ref>

On 20 June 2023, Chytil scored in a 4–1 friendly victory over [[Montenegro national football team|Montenegro]].<ref>{{Cite news|title=Čeští fotbalisté zvítězili v přípravném utkání v Černé Hoře|url=https://www.ceskenoviny.cz/zpravy/2380211|website=České Noviny|date=20 June 2023|language=cs}}</ref> Later that September, he assisted the decisive goal in a 1-1 friendly draw against [[Hungary national football team|Hungary]].<ref>{{Cite news|title=After a Draw with Czech Republic, National Team Remains Undefeated|url=https://hungarytoday.hu/after-a-draw-with-the-czech-republic-the-national-team-remains-unbeaten/|website=Hungary Today|date=11 September 2023|access-date=23 July 2024}}</ref>

On 29 May 2024, Chytil was included in the final 26-man Czech squad of the [[UEFA Euro 2024]] which would occur in June.<ref>{{Cite news|first1=Ryan|last1=Dabbs|first2=Tom|last2=Hancock|first3=Karel|last3=Herring|title=Czech Republic Euro 2024 squad: Ivan Hašek's full team|url=https://www.fourfourtwo.com/features/czech-republic-euro-2024-squad-team-players-line-up-germany|website=[[FourFourTwo]]|date=26 June 2024|access-date=23 July 2024}}</ref> Prior to the tournament, he played preparatory friendly matches against [[Malta national football team|Malta]] and [[North Macedonia national football team|North Macedonia]], scoring another [[Brace (sports)|brace]] in a thrashing 7–1 victory against the former opponent.<ref>{{Cite news|title=Czechs thump Malta 7–1 in Euro 2024 warm-up|url=https://sportstar.thehindu.com/football/international-football/czech-republic-czech-vs-malta-euro-2024-warm-up-match-result-goals-news-updates/article68264635.ece|website=sportstar.thehindu.com|date=8 June 2024}}</ref>

